						               													<description>Guns N'Bosses is a rogue-lite, cooperative, medium-weight, dice/card/bag building, board game designed by Nicolas de Tauriac and features around 80 weapons and 40 enemies illustrated by Julien Boulet.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You are mercenaries sent onto a distant planet to chase hostiles and prepare future colonisation. With the small budget allocated to this mission, you will have to find yourself some heavier weapons on the remainings of previous teams.&amp;#10;In a first part, you will encounter waves of enemies to loot. Then when you feel ready, you can confront the boss and try to defeat it !&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Choose wisely your equipement to match your gameplay but also  that of your crewmates&amp;#10;Balance your arsenal by adding or removing dices in your bag to sustain fire&amp;#10;Prepare your guns, charge them and fire them at the right moment&amp;#10;Never let down your crewmates and assist them with healing abilities or by taking shots for them&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If you enjoy rogue-lites video games, intense arena boss fight and shooter-looter, I think Guns N'Bosses is a mission for you to take on !&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
